{
  "stem": "24830.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I always went a little before or after the gestapo.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But if I was there, not only I will I have been deported, but because these false paper were empty.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I will have been tortured.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that-- you know, that was terrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I even tell-- they told you, never, never wear-- carry a list.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You have to remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Never-- and I told them, you know, if they torture me, maybe I will talk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I was not sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I could have talk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So if you want an example of what we were doing is you know the Anne Frank, Well this woman who came, and bring them all kind of thing, and talked to them-- well, that's what I was doing, except I was much younger, and I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the difference.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now, in that underground, there were some-- a few people were not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And why?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were so many-- nobody wanted to bother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First, it was dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some people didn't care.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The other thing is-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] well, I can give you-- well, sometimes they will send me to Grenoble, another part of France, where-- to get new stamp.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then I will go in the station, and-- and I bring back the stamp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it's very dangerous if they-- so I will put it-- you know, in the-- in the station in France, you have the [INAUDIBLE], a net?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then you put your luggage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So then I will put this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then if anything come, I will disappear.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I will go to another compartment, like this didn't belong to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How far did you have to go to get the stamp when you went to the other town?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, quite far.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
